name: Lunar Blessing
desc: Increases the damage dealt by attacks from Luna and nearby allied heroes. Luna is also blessed with increased vision range at night.

name: Frozen Sigil
desc: Tusk summons a Frozen Sigil by calling upon the deepest cold of winter. The Sigil creates a snowstorm which slows all enemy units within 600 range.

name: Icarus Dive
desc: Phoenix dives forward in an arc with a fixed distance in the targeted direction, dealing damage over time and slowing the movement speed of any units it comes into contact with, and then orbiting back to its original position. If Phoenix casts Supernova, the dive ends.

name: Insatiable Hunger
desc: A violent lust for vital fluids increases Broodmother's attack damage and gives her a vampiric attack.

name: Whirling Death
desc: Timbersaw whirls extremely sharp edges, damaging enemies and destroying trees around him in an area.  If an enemy hero is affected, it loses some of its primary attribute for a short duration.  Whirling Death will deal Pure damage if a tree is cut down in the process.

name: Strafe
desc: Clinkz nimbly attacks with a barrage of arrows. Dramatically increases attack speed for a short time and grants Clinkz the ability to automatically dodge projectiles.

name: Rip Tide
desc: The Naga Siren and her images hit all nearby units with a damaging wave of water that lowers armor for 8 seconds.

name: Echo Stomp
desc: Elder Titan and his Astral Spirit both stomp the ground, damaging and knocking nearby enemy units unconscious around their locations.  The Elder Titan stomp deals physical damage, while the Spirit stomp deals magical damage.

name: Jinada
desc: Bounty Hunter plans his next hit, passively adding a critical strike and maim to his next attack.

name: Ravage
desc: Slams the ground, causing tentacles to erupt in all directions, damaging and stunning all nearby enemy units.
